Titolo: Record of Lodoss War: Advent of Cardice

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Record of Lodoss War: Advent of Cardice (Record of Lodoss War in North America and Europe) is an action role-playing game developed by Neverland for the Dreamcast. It was released in Japan on June 29, 2000; in Europe on December 15, 2000; and in North America on March 14, 2001. Based on the anime series of the same name, it would be the only Lodoss video game to be released outside Japan until the release of Deedlit in Wonder Labyrinth 20 years later.

Genere: Action role-playing 

Valutazione: N/A
